videos.headline: Mizzou defeats Kansas City, records 200th home win
videos.description: Mama Dembele logs seven steals as four Tigers score in double digits, including Ashton Judd who also logged a career-high 13 rebounds, to take down the Roos, 85-42.

videos.headline: Linthacum on her new role, Mizzou's plan for SEC play
videos.description: Following her career-high 20-point effort in the win vs. Kansas City, freshman Hannah Linthacum explains the Tigers' mindset with conference play around the corner.
